Montenegro

Montenegro, officially Montenegro, is a country in Europe, with an area of 13,812 square kilometers and a population of around 622,359. Its gdp is $5,494.74 Millions(2019). The capital of Montenegro Podgorica, and the official currency is Euro(EUR).
